OL,3,CSingle police force lost 35,000 days
OL,4,Cin a year due to stress
OL,6,FPolice officers in West Yorkshire took
OL,7,Falmost 35,000 days off last year due
OL,8,Fto stress and mental health problems,
OL,9,Fan investigation by ITV Calendar has
OL,10,Ffound.
OL,12,FFigures obtained exclusively by
OL,13,FCalendar show the force - the largest
OL,14,Fin the county and the fourth biggest
OL,15,Fin the country - recorded the highest
OL,16,Fnumber of stress-related absences of
OL,17,Fany of the five forces in Yorkshire
OL,18,Fand Lincolnshire in 2023-24.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/17
