OL,6,FIn total, West Yorkshire, North
OL,7,FYorkshire, South Yorkshire, Humberside
OL,8,Fand Lincolnshire Police officers took
OL,9,Fat least 60,000 days off for mental
OL,10,Fhealth reasons - a 26% rise on five
OL,11,Fyears ago.
OL,13,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,14,Fsaid: "Exposure to traumatic events is
OL,15,Fa difficult reality for many of our
OL,16,Ffrontline workers and we never want
OL,17,Fthis to be normalised. Despite this,
OL,18,Fpolicing can still be a rewarding
OL,19,Fcareer with the right support made
OL,20,Favailable.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/17
