OL,15,FWe asked all police forces in
OL,16,FYorkshire and Lincolnshire how many
OL,17,Fdays were taken off work by officers
OL,18,Fin the last five financial years
OL,19,Fbecause of stress or other mental
OL,20,Fhealth conditions.
