OL,6,FHe was ultimately forced to give up
OL,7,Ffrontline duties and take on an
OL,8,Fadministrative role within the police
OL,9,Fafter he was run over by a drink
OL,10,Fdriver in Wakefield in July 2021.
OL,12,F"It put me in a very very dark place,"
OL,13,Fhe said. "I was up in the night
OL,14,Fcrying, sobbing, saying how am I going
OL,15,Fto get through this" he said.
OL,17,F"I've had quite a lot of therapy, CBT
OL,18,Ftherapy, which has been a massive help
OL,19,F- it's pulled me through. I think just
OL,20,Ftalking about it has helped.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/17
