OL,4,Cin a year due to stress
OL,6,F"I can openly admit today that I could
OL,7,Fhave quite easily said I've had enough
OL,8,Fbut I didn't want to give in."
OL,10,FPC Wales receives ongoing support from
OL,11,Fthe West Yorkshire Police Federation.
OL,13,FThe organisation's chair, Craig
OL,14,FNicholls, told ITV Calendar: "There's
OL,15,Fa massive amount of mental health
OL,16,Fissues within policing - from PTSD to
OL,17,Fother long term mental effects.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/17
