OL,6,F"Stephen's story is not uncommon -
OL,7,Ffrontline policing is incredibly
OL,8,Fdangerous, from going to the scene of
OL,9,Fa road traffic collision, going to a
OL,10,Fhouse fire and dragging people out,
OL,11,Fgoing to a shooting, giving first aid
OL,12,Fto adults and children.
OL,14,F"We have a finite budget and people
OL,15,Ftry their very best to work with that
OL,16,Fbudget but sometimes it's simply not
OL,17,Fenough. With the cuts, there are
OL,18,Fgenuine consequences."
