OL,6,FThe Police Treatment Centre in
OL,7,FHarrogate is one of two facilities in
OL,8,Fthe UK. Opened in 1897, it only
OL,9,Fexpanded to cover conditions like
OL,10,Fanxiety and depression in the last
OL,11,Fdecade. It now supports nearly 4,000
OL,12,Fpeople each year - one in three for
OL,13,Fmental health issues.
OL,15,FPatrick Cairns, the charity's CEO,
OL,16,Fsaid: "When I first arrived, no one
OL,17,Fwould talk about why they were here
OL,18,Fbut now you hear people all the time
OL,19,Fsay 'I'm here on the wellbeing
OL,20,Fprogramme'.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/17
