OL,6,F"Historically police felt they would
OL,7,Fbe judged if they said they had a
OL,8,Fwellbeing issue like anxiety or
OL,9,Fdepression, so it's moving but not
OL,10,Fwhere it should be."
OL,12,FThe centre in Harrogate and its
OL,13,Fcounterpart in Scotland cost more than
OL,14,F#64million combined to run. They
OL,15,Freceive no government funding and are
OL,16,Fkept afloat entirely by donations from
OL,17,Fpolice officers themselves.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/17
