OL,6,FThe clinical director, Sarah Ward,
OL,7,Fsaid: "There's fewer police to do the
OL,8,Fjob, faced with exactly the same if
OL,9,Fnot increasing trauma.
OL,11,F"Officers are sent out single crewed
OL,12,Fin cars so they face the stress of not
OL,13,Fhaving someone with you going into
OL,14,Fsomething volatile.
OL,16,F"You have that plus skeleton staffing
OL,17,Fand days off cancelled because of
OL,18,Fcivil unrest. It's relentless.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/17
