OL,6,F"In addition to that, the support that
OL,7,Fofficers used to have has also been
OL,8,Fchipped away because there's only so
OL,9,Fmuch money and that budget doesn't
OL,10,Fstretch. That money has to come from
OL,11,Fthe Home Office."
OL,13,FPolicing Minister Dame Diana Johnson
OL,14,Ftold ITV News she was extremely
OL,15,Fworried about the rise in the number
OL,16,Fof officers taking time off for their
OL,17,Fmental health.
OL,19,FShe said: "Next year there's an
OL,20,Fadditional #1billion going into
OL,21,Fpolicing, to police forces.
